-18T20:10:09.000Z","msg":"冇嘢嘅幻覺嚟嘅啫"},{"pid":"938bbec174bf6d730ba7eddee0b28a762a61448e","tid":1486192,"uid":141353,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:15:27.000Z","msg":"女人覺得另一半有野<br />\n通常都係先觀察到啲野 有跡可尋<br />\n然後形住形住有野<br />\n最後通常都中"},{"pid":"86fe7ea5fae72c77320e919d49164a07c369255a","tid":1486192,"uid":139409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:24:42.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsiukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=e6e707d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsiukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=e6e707d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"c2fbf0fcf12f7db324b38d6fa48602c5f614378c","tid":1486192,"uid":309647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"938bbec174bf6d730ba7eddee0b28a762a61448e","tid":1486192,"uid":141353,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:15:27.000Z","msg":"女人覺得另一半有野<br />\n通常都係先觀察到啲野 有跡可尋<br />\n然後形住形住有野<br />\n最後通常都中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"最賤格係會話你個人疑神疑鬼<br />\n唔相信佢，扮受害者<br />\n將個責任推落你度<br />\n令人自責將段感情搞到返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"7d208b0a695c1a81145469a35c02e4f6f3488057","tid":1486192,"uid":309647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0205f748e601208f6e398e7fa38fdda6422d1ba","tid":1486192,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:08:13.000Z","msg":"拿準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"乸<br />\n琴日太嬲唔識打無理<br />\n被分手幾日咋<br />\n已經見到佢同其他人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87749932385668e74f66e886be49a758009977c9","tid":1486192,"uid":295958,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"相信呢d賤人會有報應<br />\n祝佢地俾天收"},{"pid":"6299d2c1bcf633c302be1dc01abc8ac78a7a2e49","tid":1486192,"uid":